    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/57af2053c366b40386adf14643df321b.poster.avif?t=1771995395\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/57af2053c366b40386adf14643df321b.webm?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/57af2053c366b40386adf14643df321b.mp4?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fishing bullet hell!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 5 unique biomes with over 150+ fish to fight! Uncover new characters each with their own questlines and adventures. Complete the main quests to further your pursuit toward the kingdom, and unlock new mechanics to use throughout your adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/e14a33099a948455137817ac04f84450.poster.avif?t=1771995395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/e14a33099a948455137817ac04f84450.webm?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/e14a33099a948455137817ac04f84450.mp4?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Evolve Your Arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your adventure, you'll encounter new gameplay-changing abilities, each with unique applications, <i>hidden</i> potential, and customization paths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/752967dbf5b62630e75590aa99355ba1.poster.avif?t=1771995395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/752967dbf5b62630e75590aa99355ba1.webm?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/752967dbf5b62630e75590aa99355ba1.mp4?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Brave the Depths, Claim Your Prize</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you venture into the ocean, you'll encounter plenty of different fish, each presenting a unique challenge when hooked. While exploring the depths, you may also uncover mysterious <i>landmarks</i> waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/a248538c490ac4dd64abf2f52b39ca51.poster.avif?t=1771995395\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/a248538c490ac4dd64abf2f52b39ca51.webm?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236190/extras/a248538c490ac4dd64abf2f52b39ca51.mp4?t=1771995395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Kingdom</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Kingdom is responsible for all this madness. A machine that infected all of the land with its crystal energy and might. Thankfully, the locals are keen at taking down this force. Be alert when traveling the seas, and if you encounter them, do everything in your power to stop their presence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
